hopobject.body: I've got a part-time job amorahealth.com Apple has been expected to unveil the new iPad Mini model sometime this month, so it’ll be interesting to see what actually happens — Apple announcements are notoriously hard to nail down until shortly before they happen, if they even get spoiled beforehand at all. In other words, people can “expect” Apple to do things all they want; what Apple actually ends up doing can often end up being a different story altogether.
